    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow employees to claim unfair dismissal after probation",
        "additional_details": "Employees who have passed their probation but are short only a few days can't sue and clear their name despite having a strong case and evidence. Unfair is unfair.",
        "background": "Employees who have been dismissed can only claim for unfair dismissal if they have been in their role continuously for two years or more (except for automatically unfair reasons).",
